flowRoot.flowPara: Black on White, suitable for monochrome prints and media
Full colour, suitable for rich color prints, web, and electronic media
Monochrome logo for black / dark backgrounds for print and web media
Full colour logo for dark backgrounds for print and web media
Wide format layout for web banners, headings, poster titles, etc.

The default sans typeface is Open Sans from Google Fonts which is available free and open source under the open font license. The official logo uses Open Sans while the wide-format logo uses Open Sans Condensed Bold. "Lato", also available from Google Fonts, may be used as an alternative sans typeface. For print applications, Times New Roman, Helvetica, and Caladea (from Google Fonts) may be used.
This document is also available as an Inkscape SVG file containing all icons as layers.
Muted colour scheme, for printing on light media or high contrast applications. (00500a/951b19)
